	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Sure in the early stages of your character a mino axe, or similar, will be the best thing for you.. <BR>
<BR>
But as you go up in levels the fact that you can't harm &quot;magic&quot; creatures will render such weapons useless in too many situations.. Wisps are a good example but it doesn't stop there.  Scarecrows, Ghouls, the entire population of unrest and many, many more will be completely invulnerable unless you purchase a magic weapon.. These creatures are often where the loot and experience are..<BR>
<BR>
Don't be afraid.. Just pay the pp's and know that your now the proud owner of a &quot;serious&quot; weapon.<BR>
<BR>
Simply put, don't even bother comparing the damage stats of non magic - magic weapons.. Save yourself the embarrassment of thinking your such a smart arse to have paid so much less for your comparable weapon, only to find yourself getting torn apart by creatures that you can't even hurt back..
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
